	<purpose>
		<p>

     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of the disposition of an issue, that is, the decision on how an issue - such as a fault, problem, or unfulfillable requirement - will be resolved, either directly, through a work order to change the product, or at a later date, through a work request, or by some other action not involving a change to the product definition.
   </p>
